<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<meta name="description" content="EaglercraftX 1.8 Offline" />
<meta name="keywords" content="eaglercraft, eaglercraftx, minecraft, 1.8, 1.8.8" />
<title>UwU Client</title>
<meta property="og:locale" content="en-US" />
<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
<meta property="og:title" content="EaglercraftX 1.8 Offline" />
<meta property="og:description" content="this file is not a website, whoever uploaded it to this URL is a dumbass" />
<script type="text/javascript">
"use strict";


// %%%%%%%%% launch options %%%%%%%%%%%%

window.eaglercraftXOpts = { container: "game_frame" };

// %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%


${classes_js}

window.eaglercraftXOpts.assetsURI = ${assets_epk};

</script>

<script>

	let siteInteraction = false;

	document.addEventListener("click", () => {
		siteInteraction = true;
	});

	function updateLoadBar(size, maxSize){
		document.getElementById("loadText").innerText = "Downloading Assets... ("+Math.round(size.loaded/1024/1024)+"MB / "+Math.round(maxSize/1024/1024)+"MB)";
		let percent = Math.round(size.loaded/maxSize*100);
		document.getElementById("loadBarInside").style.width = percent+"%";
	}
	function showDecompressingAssets(){
		document.getElementById("loadBar").style.opacity = "0";
		document.getElementById("loadText").innerText = "Decompressing assets...";
	}
	function showEnableScreen(){
		document.getElementById("loadText").innerText = "Click anywhere to start UwU Client!";
		document.getElementById("loadText").style.top = "50vh";
		document.getElementById("uwuLogo").style.top = "0vh";
	}
	function showLoadingScreen(){
		document.getElementById("loadText").style.top = "72vh";
		document.getElementById("uwuLogo").style.top = "15vh";
		document.getElementById("loadText").innerText = "Loading UwU Client...";
	}
	function showMojangScreen(){
		document.getElementById("loadDiv").style.backgroundColor = "#f0323e";
		document.getElementById("loadText").style.color = "white";
		document.getElementById("uwuLogo").style.transition = "opacity 0.2s";
		document.getElementById("uwuLogo").style.opacity = "0";
		document.getElementById("mojangLogo").style.opacity = "1";
	}

	function getSiteInteraction(){
		return siteInteraction;
	}

	function die(){
		document.getElementById("mojangLogo").style.transition = "top 0.4s";
		document.getElementById("mojangLogo").style.top = "30vh";
		document.getElementById("loadText").style.transition = "opacity 0.2s";
		document.getElementById("loadText").style.opacity = "0";
		setTimeout(()=> {
			document.getElementById("mojangLogo").style.transition = "height 0.6s, top 0.6s";
			document.getElementById("mojangLogo").style.height = "120vh";
			document.getElementById("mojangLogo").style.top = "-13vh";
			document.getElementById("loadDiv").style.transition = "opacity 0.4s";
			document.getElementById("loadDiv").style.opacity = "0";
			setTimeout(()=> {
				document.getElementById("loadDiv").style.display = "none";
			},400);
		},400);
	}
</script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="classes.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="fix-webm-duration.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	"use strict";
	window.addEventListener("load", () => {
			
			main();
	});
</script>
<style>
	#loadText{
		font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
		text-align: center;
		position: absolute;
		top: 72vh;
		left: 50vw;
		transform: translate(-50%);
		transition: color, top 0.4s;
	}
	#uwuLogo{
		position: relative;
		left: 50vw;
		transform: translate(-50%);
		top: 15vh;
		height: 500px;
		transition: top 0.4s;
	}
	#mojangLogo{
		position: absolute;
		left: 50vw;
		transform: translate(-50%);
		filter: invert(100%);
		top: 27vh;
		height: 300px;
		transition: opacity 0.4s;
		opacity: 0;
	}
	#loadBar{
		width: 80vw;
		height: 25px;
		border: 4px solid black;
		border-radius: 50px;
		top: 80vh;
		left: 50vw;
		transform: translate(-50%);
		position: absolute;
		transition: opacity 0.4s;
	}
	#loadBarInside{
		height: 100%;
		width: 0%;
		border-radius: 50px;
		background-color: black;
		transition: width 0.2s;
	}
</style>


<link type="image/png" rel="shortcut icon" href="data:image/png;base64," />
</head>
<body style="margin:0px;width:100vw;height:100vh;overflow:hidden;" id="game_frame">
	<div id="loadDiv" style="background-color: white; width: 100vw; height: 100vh; z-index: 1; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; transition: opacity, background-color 0.4s;">
		<img id="uwuLogo" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"></img>
		<img id="mojangLogo" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,">
		<h2 id="loadText">Loading...</h2>
		<div id="loadBar">
			<div id="loadBarInside"></div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
